@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vbcllm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.98
    v2 = 0.05
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.51)) * ((tmp + 0.56 * v1 + 0.68) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.47)))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v1 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.71 + tmp + 0.86) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(v2) + ((v2 + 0.52 / v2 + 0.78) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
